name: SAS ATR 72, Economy Class from Gothenburg to Copenhagen
description:
In this video, join me on a 55 minute flight between Gothenburg Landvetter, Sweden and Copenhagen Kastrup, Denmark. This was my first flight with SAS and I was impressed.

I really liked their lounge concept, which you will see towards the start of the video.

The flight was operated by a Jet Time ATR 72, my favourite short haul prop aircraft. Enjoy the video, leave a comment and SUBSCRIBE! Thank you!
